This paper discusses the use of cloud-based techniques to enhance the performance and energy efficiency of mobile networks. Specifically, it focuses on the joint energy minimization and resource allocation in C-RAN with MCC. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Other likely categories include cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
